        " \n \nSENIOR MANAGER GRIDS-TRANSMISSION-APOLLO CONVERTOR STATION-NEAR PRETORIA (INTERNAL AND EXTERNAL)\nVacancy type: Executive\nTask Grade : E-Band\nArea of Specialization : Reporting to the General Manager Grids, the Senior Manager Grids (Apollo & WPCS) will be responsible to provide strategic leadership, direction and other resources for the safe operation, maintenance and restoration of plant and networks.\nDepartment : Ops and Maintenance\nBusiness Unit : Apollo Grid\nLocation : South Africa (Gauteng)\nReference Number : Tx-Exec50027415\nClosing Date : 12/1/2023\n \nMinimum Requirements\n\nQualification(s):  \nB Degree in Electrical Engineering at a NQF level 7 with 360 credits\nB Tech in Electrical Engineering at a NQF 7 level with 360 credits\nA Government Certificate of Competency (GCC), and/or Professional registration with Engineering Council of South Africa (ECSA) as a Pr. Eng Engineer will be an added advantage.\n\nExperience:\n10 Years extensive experience in Power Systems in general, preferably within the wires environment (i.e., Transmission and Distribution)\nKnowledge and/or understanding of HVDC Systems\n \nSkills and Competencies\n\nBehavioural:\nIntegrity, honesty, trustworthiness, professionalism\nStrong drive to learn\nBe results and delivery focused\nBe able to work as part of a team\nIntegrity\nSafety consciousness\nProfessionalism\n\nLeadership:\nLive the Eskom vision and values\nGrow people, coaching and mentoring\nIgnite passion, motivating teams\nPromote teamwork and be able to works as part of a team\nEncourage the right behaviour\nPromote open and transparent communication\nStrong communication skills, entrepreneurial mind-set\nAbility to build effective relationships and delivery on expectations\n\nKnowledge:\nProject management knowledge and exposure\nOperational experience at network level\nSound knowledge of the Eskom and Transmission business\nRisk management\nDemand management\nBroad technical knowledge\n\nSkills:\nPeople management\nFinancial and General Business management\nEffective resource management skills\nNegotiation skill\n \nKey Responsibilities\nProvide direction and leadership to ensure strategic and operational performance of the Grid.\nProvide strategic technical leadership of the wires business in the Grid.\nManagement of plant and technology network integrity.\nDrive the Safety and the Environment practices within the Grid.\nProvide strategic leadership and direction to Projects.\nEstablish internal and external stakeholder relationship management.\nProvide strategic management of the Grid Business Area.\n \nPLEASE APPLY HERE\n \n \n \n ",
